<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Verify Your Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .box {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .otp {
        font-size: 1.4em;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 16px 0;
        color: #4f8cff;
      }
      .note {
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="box">
      <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
      <p>Use the OTP below to verify your account:</p>
      <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p>
      <p>This code will expire in 2 hours.</p>
      <p>If you didn’t sign up, you can ignore this email.</p>
      <div class="note">— Note Taking App Team</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
